sequenceDiagram
  %% Basis: official architecture page. Job schema and failure behavior pending source verification.
  participant Scheduler
  participant Jobs as jobs.json
  participant Agent as Fresh AIAgent
  participant Skills as Attached Skills
  participant Delivery
  participant Platform

  Scheduler->>Jobs: load due jobs
  Scheduler->>Agent: create fresh agent
  Scheduler->>Skills: inject attached skills as context
  Skills-->>Agent: skill context
  Agent-->>Scheduler: job response
  Scheduler->>Delivery: send result
  Delivery->>Platform: platform message
  Scheduler->>Jobs: update state and next_run

